TaxonJSON is like GeoJSON, just for Taxa

3 required attributes, unlimited optional attributes

"taxon" : {} is for definition parameters

example:

{
	"taxon_source" : "taxonomy.sources.col",   // required
	"name_uuid" : "6bed6dce-18ab-492c-a0ee-6d0d4e2a30d8",   // required
	"taxon_latname" : "Turdus merula", // required
	"taxon_author" : "someone 1982", // required
	"taxon_nuid" : "001001", // required
	"gbifNubkey" : "239r6723985" // optional
	...
}
